      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s mostly that resultsink can then call UpdateInvocation to update the fields.\n\nI thought about doing this in CreateTestResult/BatchCreateTestResults, but by then such info is already buried in test results, and to pick them out would be pre-computation.",
